spirit:hwParameter.spirit:prompt: AXI and AHBL Clock Domains are Asynchronous
Select RAM Type Inferred for internal FIFOs
Expose WID outside AXI Slave Bus Interface

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:script: Enable('EXPOSE_WID', And(Eq('AXI_SEL_MM_S', 'AXI Slave BIF'), Eq('AXI_INTERFACE', 'AXI3 Interface')));\

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: The CoreAXItoAHBL is an AXI3/AXI4 slave and an AHBL master that provides an interface (bridge) between the AXI domain and AHB domain. The CoreAXItoAHBL allows an AXI bus system to be connected to an AHB bus system. The AXI to AHB Bridge enables the AXI master to communicate with AHB slave. It allows the AXI bus to initiate data transfer between the two buses.
